- level design

refactoring:
- terrain triggers, blocks, polyominos sinking
- start_move finish_move, terrain_trigger_test terrain_trigger_action


features:
- effects
	- color
	- show when a dead-key command is pending
	- pause momentarily after your move before enemies move
- graphics
	- tile based
	- polyomino effects
